{"tid":2018320,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中央：中國公務員年收入平均達90501元人民幣","createTime":"2020-05-15T14:10:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T15:47:34.000Z","uid":98317,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"76828f2208967d7db9b5e04fc0558be35f70a386","tid":2018320,"uid":98317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:10:38.000Z","msg":"城鎮非私營單位年平均工資超9萬元#】國家統計局15日發佈#2019年平均工資。2019年<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">全國城鎮非私營單位</span></span></strong>就業人員年平均工資為90501元，比上年增長9.8%，扣除價格因素，實際增長6.8%； <span style=\"color: blue;\">城鎮私營單位就業人員年平均工資為53604元</span>比上年增長8.1%，扣除價格因素，實際增長5.2%。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQJeTEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQJeTEN.jpg&h=d89ca589&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ysTOdEN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FysTOdEN.jpg&h=1c6a5650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sbtVC6s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsbtVC6s.jpg&h=10217337&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bh7uc7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bh7uc7.jpg&h=2083d809&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e2c9a1bd6b655f5fa303ef6ad86a47e3ebc51b32","tid":2018320,"uid":69864,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:42:10.000Z","msg":"中南海人均收入？<br />\n有錢佬（千萬收入以上）＋中南海服侍佢地既工人（一個有錢佬：100個工人）<br />\n除人頭可能有９萬唔出奇"},{"pid":"8cc3be2a4b445450d2a75e9c11d9c4dbddf31b73","tid":2018320,"uid":1095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T14:44:44.000Z","msg":"維尼都冇咁高<br />\n公墓員應該自我減薪"},{"pid":"d551a668cf070f5fc8390bdd887b5c53b92d54a0","tid":2018320,"uid":205469,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T15:16:05.000Z","msg":"林鄭半個月嘅人工都多過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosa